TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT LKP_DEMO_SRC.DW_SRC_ID as DW_SRC_ID, LKP_DEMO_SRC.PRO_SRC_ID_PK as PRO_SRC_ID_PK, LKP_DEMO_SRC.PRO_SRC_POL_ID as PRO_SRC_POL_ID, LKP_DEMO_SRC.ID_TYP as ID_TYP, LKP_DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_X as POLICY_NBR_X, LKP_DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_SEQ as POLICY_NBR_SEQ, LKP_DEMO_SRC.C_ID as C_ID -- from $$VAR1.LKP_DEMO_SRC LKP_DEMO_SRC JOIN TGR2.DEMO_TGT1 p ON LKP_DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_X = p.POLICY_NBR_X and LKP_DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_SEQ = p.POLICY_NBR_SEQ --

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: ID_TYP = ID_TYP_i AND POLICY_NBR_X = POLICY_NBR_X_i AND POLICY_NBR_SEQ = POLICY_NBR_SEQ_i AND C_ID = C_ID_i

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DEMO_SRC.MC_ID, DEMO_SRC.CT_ID, DEMO_SRC.C_ID, CONVERT(datetime2, DEMO_SRC.LAST_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP) as LAST_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP , DEMO_SRC.EFFECTIVE_D, DEMO_SRC.EXPIRATION_D, DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_X, DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_SEQ, DEMO_SRC.SRC_POL_ID, DEMO_SRC4.TRANSACTION_TYPE_C, DEMO_SRC4.TRANSACTION_STATUS FROM TGR.DEMO_SRC DEMO_SRC JOIN TGR.DEMO_SRC1 DEMO_SRC1 ON DEMO_SRC1.MC_ID = DEMO_SRC.MC_ID AND DEMO_SRC1.CT_ID = DEMO_SRC.CT_ID JOIN TGR.DEMO_SRC2 DEMO_SRC2 ON DEMO_SRC2.MC_ID = DEMO_SRC.MC_ID AND DEMO_SRC2.CT_ID = DEMO_SRC.CT_ID JOIN TGR.DEMO_SRC3 DEMO_SRC3 ON DEMO_SRC3.MC_ID = DEMO_SRC.MC_ID AND DEMO_SRC3.CT_ID = DEMO_SRC.CT_ID JOIN TGR.DEMO_SRC4 DEMO_SRC4 ON DEMO_SRC4.MC_ID = DEMO_SRC.MC_ID AND DEMO_SRC4.CT_ID = DEMO_SRC.CT_ID --WHERE $$FILTER WHERE CONVERT(datetime2, DEMO_SRC.LAST_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP) BETWEEN CONVERT(datetime2, '$$DATA_START_DTTM') and CONVERT(datetime2, '$$DATA_END_DTTM') AND ( DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_X is not null AND SUBSTRING( DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_X,4,1) <> 'Q') AND (DEMO_SRC1.REMOVAL_CODE is NULL or DEMO_SRC1.REMOVAL_CODE <> 'D') AND DEMO_SRC4.TRANSACTION_TYPE_C not in('NONRENEW','PENDCA','BACKOUT','RWLEXISTS','FRS') AND (DEMO_SRC4.TRANSACTION_STATUS = 'O' AND DEMO_SRC4.TRANSACTION_TYPE_C in ('NB','RENEW','REWRITE','CONV') AND DEMO_SRC4.QT_APP_POL_C <> 'REINSTATE_WITH_LAPSE') AND DEMO_SRC4.RATING_TIME_STAMP IS NOT NULL ORDER BY DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_X, DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_SEQ,DEMO_SRC.LAST_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DEMO_SRC.MC_ID, DEMO_SRC.CT_ID, DEMO_SRC.C_ID, CONVERT(datetime2, DEMO_SRC.LAST_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP) as LAST_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP , DEMO_SRC.EFFECTIVE_D, DEMO_SRC.EXPIRATION_D, DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_X, DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_SEQ, DEMO_SRC.SRC_POL_ID, DEMO_SRC4.TRANSACTION_TYPE_C, DEMO_SRC4.TRANSACTION_STATUS FROM TGR.DEMO_SRC DEMO_SRC JOIN TGR.DEMO_SRC1 DEMO_SRC1 ON DEMO_SRC1.MC_ID = DEMO_SRC.MC_ID AND DEMO_SRC1.CT_ID = DEMO_SRC.CT_ID JOIN TGR.DEMO_SRC2 DEMO_SRC2 ON DEMO_SRC2.MC_ID = DEMO_SRC.MC_ID AND DEMO_SRC2.CT_ID = DEMO_SRC.CT_ID JOIN TGR.DEMO_SRC3 DEMO_SRC3 ON DEMO_SRC3.MC_ID = DEMO_SRC.MC_ID AND DEMO_SRC3.CT_ID = DEMO_SRC.CT_ID JOIN TGR.DEMO_SRC4 DEMO_SRC4 ON DEMO_SRC4.MC_ID = DEMO_SRC.MC_ID AND DEMO_SRC4.CT_ID = DEMO_SRC.CT_ID --WHERE $$FILTER WHERE CONVERT(datetime2, DEMO_SRC.LAST_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP) BETWEEN CONVERT(datetime2, '$$DATA_START_DTTM') and CONVERT(datetime2, '$$DATA_END_DTTM') AND ( DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_X is not null AND SUBSTRING( DEMO_SRC.POLICY_NBR_X,4,1) <> 'Q') AND (DEMO_SRC1.REMOVAL_CODE is NULL or DEMO_SRC1.REMOVAL_CODE <> 'D') AND DEMO_SRC4.TRANSACTION_TYPE_C not in('NONRENEW','PENDCA','BACKOUT','RWLEXISTS','FRS') AND DEMO_SRC4.TRANSACTION_STATUS = 'C' ORDER BY DEMO_SRC.MC_ID,DEMO_SRC.CT_ID,DEMO_SRC.LAST_UPDATE_TIMESTAMP

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CONCAT(YEAR(DEMO_SRC1.EFF_DATE), FORMAT(DATEPART (DY ,DEMO_SRC1.EFF_DATE),'000'), '000') + CASE WHEN DEMO_SRC1.removal_code = 'U' and CONTRACT_TRANSACTION2.ct_type in ('PC','CA') THEN DEMO_SRC1.PREV_CT_ID ELSE DEMO_SRC1.CT_ID END as POL_STATE_VRSN, -- DEMO_SRC1.MC_ID as MC_ID, DEMO_SRC1.CT_ID as CT_ID -- FROM $$SCHEMA_OWNER.DEMO_SRC1 DEMO_SRC1 join $$SCHEMA_OWNER.DEMO_SRC1 CONTRACT_TRANSACTION2 on CONTRACT_TRANSACTION2.MC_ID = DEMO_SRC1.MC_ID and CONTRACT_TRANSACTION2.CT_ID = CASE WHEN DEMO_SRC1.reversing_transaction is null THEN DEMO_SRC1.CT_ID ELSE DEMO_SRC1.reversing_transaction END WHERE DEMO_SRC1.ct_type not in ('PENDCA','NONRENEW') ORDER BY MC_ID, CT_ID, POL_STATE_VRSN --
